body:
J. Edgar Hoover Building, 935 Pennsylvania

170096785641

Avenue, NW Washington, D.C. 20535.

                     APPROVED REFUND OF SCAM VICTIM’S FUNDS:

We are here to inform you that we have been able to trap down some of the
scam artists which have been terrorizing the general public in the name of
helping our individuals to get their benefit fund or to indulge into
business with them with the aim of defrauding the general public.
Upon the course of our investigations, we found some documents bearing your
name and your email address in the computer hard disk of the scammers.
Having reported this matter to the World Bank president (Jim Yong Kim), who
instructed that the assets confiscated from the scammers should be shared
to those that their name and email addresses was found in the possession of
the scam artists as a refund of loosed money in the form of cash payment
which you are among.



*You are therefore to be compensated with the sum of $900,000.00 United
States Dollars.*

Also, we arrested some men who claimed to be bank officials, Contract
managers, Barristers and Lottery Agents who has been sending you bogus
letters and SMS via your telephone numbers and Facebook indicating that you
have won a lottery which does not exist, claiming to release fund to you
via ATM CARD,BANK TRANSFER,DIPLOMATIC MEANS OF PAYMENT COURIER SERVICE
DELIVERY COMPANY proposing business which does not exist and those using
different Bank names to scam the general public.

Below is the link of the arrested fraudsters for your perusal.

 *ttp://nakedsecurity.sophos.com/2020/07/27/fbi-arrests-24-in-internet-credit-card-fraud-ring/

Therefore, you are to contact the Deputy Governor of Islamic Bank on this
email:

*remittancebk@usa.com <remittancebk@usa.com>* With the below information
for his verification and instructions to guide you on the refund process of
your money, as he is in position to notify your bank for immediate
crediting of this fund to your local bank account because the United
Nations Anti-Crime Commission, International Monetary Fund (IMF) and the
World bank has chosen them to payout all the compensation funds to the
victims.

Warning: You are to stop all communications you are having with any
person/persons, claiming to be agent, investor or bank officials in Africa,
Europe (London) and Asia regarding any form of release of funds to you as
their aim is to defraud you.

subject: Re: Do you receive your scam com
body:
Hello Mr. Michael Bricks,

Thank you for reaching out to me and providing this information. It's quite concerning to hear about these scam artists and their attempts to defraud the general public. I appreciate your efforts in tracking them down.

Could you please provide me with more details about how exactly my name and email address ended up in the possession of these scammers? I'm curious to know if there was a specific incident or if it was just a random occurrence.

Also, could you clarify how the refund process works? You mentioned that I am entitled to a sum of United States Dollars, but I would like to understand the steps involved in receiving this refund. Is there any paperwork or verification process that needs to be completed?

Lastly, I noticed that you mentioned contacting the Deputy Governor of Islamic Bank for further guidance. Could you please provide me with their contact information so that I can reach out to them directly?

Thank you once again for bringing this matter to my attention. I look forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Andree
